column5: Looking for a decent resort that has 3 bed 2 bath cabin. we are three couples that have fished Canada for a long time and looking for new resort. Primarily fish for walleyes. want a lake that has good fishing.
stay away from dryden,far away,if you cant drink the water ,why would you eat the fish
Check out Fisherman's Cove Resort on Lac Seul Lake. Awesome Walleye fishing & they have a cabin #7 that meets your needs! http://www.lacseulfishermanscove.com/index.html RBF
Just got back from there. Cabin 5, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, Easy to drive to, nice people.
www.birchdalelodge.com on Eagle Lake 807-227-5262 Cabin #1 is a 3 bedroom 2 bathroom that was built last year.
You might want to check with John: You can also fish Lac Seul if you want to trailer a short distance......http://www.fishredpine.com/at-the-lodge
